    "description": "《一抹紫色》是一部讲述艺术与酷儿爱情的短篇电子小说。你将跟随曾经走红现已瘫痪的画家玛雅，看她怎样竭力接受现实，现实又如何影响她的恋情，顺带和你的前额叶皮质斗嘴，使一位艺评人受辱，并与老人结成忘年交。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>短暂而甜蜜的游戏体验，尊重你的时间（时长40分钟~1小时）</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396620/extras/ea816fcc902ef69e1742070d32d5aba9.avif?t=1727311822\" width=620 height=240 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>参与玛雅内心的挣扎，与她的前额叶皮质对话，以独特的内省视角审视她的心理状态</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396620/extras/5f50b4cb716d2883417b2ef635bdd6d5.avif?t=1727311822\" width=620 height=240 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>情感丰沛的酷儿故事，以电子小说的形式呈现</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396620/extras/0c86178a00d3d8a1d1dd8a7d8deb3bba.avif?t=1727311822\" width=620 height=240 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>听形形色色的角色从各自的视角讲述他们自己的故事</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396620/extras/aa05473d763b246097e310c9e79465af.avif?t=1727311822\" width=620 height=240 /></span><br><br><strong>《一抹紫色》汉译版附录： ，内含译注</strong><br><i>S. Chinese Localization by EchoriverTranslators 回声河翻译组.</i>",
